title: TNF Recap: Texans At Chiefs
itunes:title: TNF Recap: Texans At Chiefs
description:
A full room of heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the first game of the 2020 season between the Super Bowl Champs (Chiefs- for those living under a rock) and the Houston Texans. With no preseason and an unconventional offseason, Thursday Night Football delivered a kicking start to the 2020 season.
